name: GoWatchIt
0:
”Alexa, open Go Watch It and ask where I can watch 8 mile.”
”Alexa, open Go Watch It.”
”Alexa, ask Go Watch It if 8 Mile is available on Netflix.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: go watch it
des: The GoWatchIt skill helps you find out where your movie is available online - Including all of your preferred platforms and services for online streaming, digital rent or purchase. It also sends direct links to your Alexa app for each viewing option, so you can quickly find the movie on your preferred platform.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
